🐺 The Alpha's Dispatch — v1.1.0

The pack grows stronger. The Bell tolls for new territory.

─── ADDED ───
• Bell-based territory claiming — place a Bell to found a faction and claim 5×5 chunks
• 10-chunk sanctuary buffer between all faction territories
• /f setspawn — the Alpha marks the pack's sacred ground
• /f spawn — any pup can return to the den
• /f disband — the Alpha dissolves the pack and releases all claims
• Particle trail guidance — the spirits show the way to safe ground
• Bell interaction messages now speak the faction's name

─── CHANGED ───
• Faction founding now requires a Bell to claim territory
• Block protection messages updated for Bell blocks

─── FIXED ───
• Faction claims no longer encroach on neighboring territories
